{
  "stem": "3165.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And see, like, I think it was probably a bigger shock for my sister to see me, because I knew I was looking for her.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think she was in shock, sort of, like, couldn't believe it, that-- that here I am, that it's me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She looked so frail and so-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, so-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] but she was alive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that, to me, was the main thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went back to Korzec and didn't go to the Primacs right away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I think what happened-- my sister wasn't feeling good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was still a long way to go to the Primacs' house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So again, some Jewish people were there, and they told me we can stay there, you know, till my sister feels better.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then my sister, the next day, got very sick, again, with-- also with high fever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I really think it was because from the shock, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She got very sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they let us stay there for a few days till she got better.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And after that, we went to the Primacs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they, of course, couldn't believe it, that I came with-- that I found my sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, well, you can stay here with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the war was still going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't finished yet, right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, in Korzec, now, from there, they wanted to move to a bigger city, going west, closer to Poland, because now it's Russia, for sure.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only fighting was, you know, like, I guess, Ukrainian police [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were looking-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how did it go?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, for Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them were injured, and they came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
